Package: krrr
Type: Package
Title: Kernel Ridge Riesz Regression
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alejandro", "Schuler", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alejandro.schuler@gmail.com")
Description: R wrapper around the Python 'krrr' package — kernel ridge
    regression for the Riesz representer of a linear functional. Sister
    package to 'rieszboost'. Reuses 'rieszboost' for estimand specification
    and the augmentation engine; swaps in a kernel solver for the actual fit.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    R6,
    reticulate (>= 1.30),
    rieszreg (>= 0.0.1)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    pkgload
Config/testthat/edition: 3
